    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic find! This vehicle is in truly good condition, having been well-cared for and maintained with regular service. While it shows a few light signs of its journey so far, it remains a reliable, stylish, and comfortable ride that's ready for many more miles. It's the perfect balance of quality and value for anyone looking for a dependable car they can be proud of!",
      "price": 34500.0,
