    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require extensive mechanical work to be roadworthy again. The engine is currently misfiring and running very roughly, while the transmission shows significant slipping and hesitation. Additionally, there is noticeable body rust and the interior upholstery is heavily worn. This is an ideal project car for a mechanic or someone looking for a source of spare parts.",
