      "description": "Presenting a truly exemplary specimen of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been maintained to an uncompromising standard since its inception. Every surface reflects a rigorous commitment to preservation, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, meticulously kept interior. Mechanically, the vehicle operates with absolute precision, offering a driving experience that mirrors its original delivery state. This is an investment-grade acquisition for the discerning individual who demands nothing less than the definitive standard in pre-owned luxury.",
      "price": 44900.0,
